docs.title: HMIS Data Standards
docs.text: Welcome! This site is a single source of truth for HUD HMIS data definitions.

docs.title: 📋 Data Dictionary
docs.text: A structured list of all HMIS data elements and definitions.

docs.title: 📊 Value Lists
docs.text: Reusable code sets (like bed types, yes/no lists, etc.) used by multiple elements.

docs.title: 📌 How to use
docs.text:
• Explore the left sidebar
  • Search by element ID or field name
  • Click any item to see details
